The primary purpose of our proposed model is to route optimization & planning by analyzing the micro-level delivery based on specified location using Computer simulation. This framework (Figure 1) from distribution centre to delivery location based on delivery sequence consists of two major steps-1) Agent-base behaviour Analysis using GIS  allocated Location at El Paso and 2) Developing and implementing DES Simulation to ensure the delivery to the location (House, Apt, Company) at Step-1 using collected from MOST analysis.
